---
title: Winter Risotto with Wilted Kale, Roasted Tomatoes and Parmesan Cheese
description: Hearty kale pairs perfectly with nutty Parmesan and crunchy walnuts for a warm and wintery dish. The fennel seeds add a unique flavour which is a subtle addition to this meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/risotto-dhiver-f93d3d68.jpg
